Download:
	http://numpy.scipy.org/

General:
See below for details on LAPACK/BLAS. 

	python setup.py build --help-fcompiler

will tell you what fortran compilers were found.

	rm -fr build
	python setup.py build --fcompiler=...   (e.g., intelem for ifort-64)
	python setup.py install
	
Note, a bug in numpy prevents --fcompiler=... to be used with "install".
Build first then install.

####################################
# BLAS / LAPACK
#

atlas:
 	python setup.py install

mkl / ifort:
        copy site.cfg_mkl_9-11 to site.cfg
	edit to get correct path to mkl
	python setup.py install
 
